## Ratings Create [/ratings]
### Create a Rating [POST]
+ Request (application/json)

    
        {
            name: "R"
            minimum_age: 17

        }

        

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        { 
          data: {
            modified_by: null
            name: "R"
