          }
        }

## Rating [/ratings/id]
Get a single Rating object 
+ Parameters
    + id (required, number, `1`) ... Numeric `id` of the Rating to perform action with.

### Retrieve a Rating [GET]
+ Response 200 (application/json)

    + Body

            {
                data: {
                  modified_by: null
                  name: "PG"
                  minimum_age: 10
                  created_at: "2014-03-25T21:30:42+00:00"
                  updated_at: "2014-03-25T21:30:42+00:00"
                  class: "Rating"
                  version: 1
                  modifier: null
                  id: 1
                }
            }
            
### Update A Rating [PATCH]

+ Request (application/json)

        {
            first_name: "R"
        }
+ Response 200 (application/json)

        {
            data : {
              modified_by: null
              name: "R"
              minimum_age: 10
              created_at: "2014-03-25T21:30:42+00:00"
              updated_at: "2014-03-25T21:30:42+00:00"
              class: "Rating"
              version: 2
              modifier: null
              id: 1
            }
        }   

